org.apache.ignite.spi.discovery

Interface DiscoverySpiDataExchange


  • public interface DiscoverySpiDataExchange
    Handler for initial data exchange between Ignite nodes. Data exchange is initiated by a new node when it tries to join topology and finishes before it actually joins.

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      Map<Integer,Serializable> collect(UUID joiningNodeId)
      Collects data from all components.
      void onExchange(UUID joiningNodeId, UUID nodeId, Map<Integer,Serializable> data)
      Notifies discovery manager about data received from remote node.

    • Method Detail

      • collect

        Map<Integer,Serializable> collect(UUID joiningNodeId)
        Collects data from all components. This method is called both on new node that joins topology to transfer its data to existing nodes and on all existing nodes to transfer their data to new node.
        Parameters:
        joiningNodeId - ID of new node that joins topology.
        Returns:
        Collection of discovery data objects from different components.

      • onExchange

        void onExchange(UUID joiningNodeId,
              UUID nodeId,
              Map<Integer,Serializable> data)
        Notifies discovery manager about data received from remote node.
        Parameters:
        joiningNodeId - ID of new node that joins topology.
        nodeId - ID of the node provided data.
        data - Collection of discovery data objects from different components.
